<note n="0333001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0333001">過去二十四佛中不見此尊之名，諒係指辟支佛？</note>
<note n="0335001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0335001">從暹羅本為 Upāhanadāyaka。</note>
<note n="0336001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0336001">Jotiya（光輝）。</note>
<note n="0337001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0337001">aggaja「第一生」之義，此處或為花名。</note>
<note n="0337002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0337002">Amita（無量）。</note>
<note n="0338001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0338001">Bhikha（施食）應指為 Ekāsanadāyaka 長老。</note>
